Broccoli Hash Recipe

Haf lb Broccoli (Chopped)
3 Tbsp Butter
Half Tbsp Red Pepper Flakes
4 Eggs
Half lb Bacon
1 Cup Arugula
Salt and Pepper to Taste
1 Med Onion Chopped
2 tsp Garlic chopped

Cook and Drain Bacon. Set Aside to cool. Chop once cool

Melt Butter in Pan. Add Onion. Cook until Tender

Add Broccoli and Garlic. Cook 10 Mins until tender

Add arugula, Red Pepper, salt and pepper. Reducee heat and stir until 
Arugula is wilted

Make Wells in mix. Add eggs in wells. Cover and cook to desired level.

Add crumbled bacon and serve warm